From: James Clark <james.clark@linaro.org>
Date: Wed, 8 Jan 2025 14:28:58 +0000
Subject: perf tools arm-spe: Pull out functions for aux buffer and tracking
 setup
Git-commit: 23a65c5e8b18c01de31f8b849cb3fbaaacaffe5b
Patch-mainline: v6.14-rc1
References: perf-sle16.1-v6.19-userspace-update

These won't be used in the next commit in discard mode, so put them in
their own functions. No functional changes intended.

